Return MASK_TYPE_NO_SUPPORT, MASK_TYPE_MASK or MASK_TYPE_GROUP
if 'Group Masking and Mapping' profile is supported, return
MASK_TYPE_GROUP

If raise_error == False, just return MASK_TYPE_NO_SUPPORT
or, raise NO_SUPPORT error.
